Joining the show is Brandon Toy, a former soldier turned defense contractor who is now a conscientious objector. Self-described as being "ignorant, naÃƒÂ¯ve, and misled" at the time of his military enlistment in 2003, Toy recently resigned from his project management position at General Dynamics in complete objection to drone warfare and our loss of due process under the NDAA. 

Privacy advocate and talk show host Dr. Katherine Albrecht also joins the show to provide more updates on Internet spying as well as a discussion on cancer remedies.
